## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **vorasidenib Voranigo 2024** = first FDA IDH1/IDH2 dual inhibitor + first FDA grade 2 glioma drug. INDIGO Phase 3 (Mellinghoff 2023 NEJM) PFS HR 0.39. paradigm shift — 25 years 만에 GBM-only era 종료. quantum-VQE 의 IDH1 R132H + IDH2 R140Q dual pocket fit.
2. **temozolomide Temodar 1999 + Stupp 2005** = first FDA GBM + 만성 alkylating 1L 25+ year. RT + TMZ concurrent + adjuvant → mOS 14.6 → 20+ month MGMT-methylated. 만성 alkylating O6-methylguanine + MGMT repair quantum-VQE 직접 fit.
3. **bevacizumab Avastin 2009** = first FDA recurrent GBM — anti-angiogenesis. PFS gain 명확 but OS gain 미확인 (RTOG 0825 + AVAglio 2014). pseudoresponse + edema 감소 분리 어려움.
4. **TTF Optune 2015/2018** = first FDA tumor-treating fields device — non-drug 200 kHz alternating electric field. EF-14 trial + mOS 20.9 (TMZ+TTF) vs 16.0 (TMZ only). compliance + cost + 머리 면도 limitation. quantum 직접 fit 없음.
5. **DCVax-L Northwest Bio 2023 Phase 3 + 2024 EU approval** = autologous DC + tumor lysate vaccine. Liau 2023 JAMA Oncol — mOS 19.3 newly diagnosed + 13.2 recurrent. external control + design 비판 + EU MAA 2024 approval. US FDA 미정.
6. **CAR-T (EGFRvIII + IL13Rα2 + B7-H3 + GD2) research 다수** = 만성 GBM cell therapy 미해결. EGFRvIII CAR-T (Penn 2017 Sci Transl Med) antigen escape. Choi 2024 NEJM EGFRvIII CAR-T + bivalent intrathecal — early signal. cross-cell_therapy_platform.
7. **ONC201 + ONC206 H3K27M DMG** = pediatric DMG/DIPG (diffuse intrinsic pontine glioma) — DRD2 antagonist + ClpP agonist. ONC201 expanded access + Phase 3 ACTION trial 진행. 만성 pediatric brainstem glioma 의 미해결 first-in-class signal.
8. **BBB-cross paradigm — focused ultrasound + RMT shuttle + nanoparticle** = 만성 brain pharmacology bottleneck. Exablate Neuro + SonoCloud temporary BBB disruption. Denali / Roche brain shuttle TfR / IGF1R RMT. 만성 nanoparticle (AGuIX gadolinium polysiloxane radiosensitizer cross-precision_radiation_onc).
9. **immune checkpoint (nivolumab + ipilimumab + pembrolizumab) GBM 부정 결과** = CheckMate 143/498/548 OS 차이 없음. cold tumor + lymphocyte-depleted TME + low TMB. mismatch repair-deficient subset (small) + neoadjuvant pembrolizumab Cloughesy 2019 small benefit signal. quantum-VQE 직접 fit 한정.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, glioma + GBM 임상 의미 한정. 만성 BBB-cross + 만성 paradigm 의 in-silico shortcut → in-vivo validation gap 매우 큼.

